{"tid":946611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓粉上機追星後即走人累街坊 大韓航空下月起罰退票客$1,400","createTime":"2018-12-18T15:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T04:51:30.000Z","uid":41818,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"21ee8a2aa4acf668b465ab01e82eb34748e4354e","tid":946611,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181218/large/1545136224_5ed6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181218%2Flarge%2F1545136224_5ed6.png&h=f0dda3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由下月起，大韓航空向所有已辦理離境手續、但取消乘搭的國際航班乘客，收取約1,385元港幣的額外罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上周六（15日），數名追星族為於禁區內見偶像，在購買機票並登機後，即以急事為由落機及退票，令全機乘客需落機及重新接受安檢，航班最終延誤約1小時。 大韓航空今日（18日）發聲明指，為針對近日的事故，由下年1月1日起，將向所有已辦理離境手續、但取消乘搭的國際航班乘客，收取200,000韓圜（約1,400元港幣）的額外罰款。<br />\n<br />\n大韓航空稱，近日發現有人濫用低罰款措施和免罰款的預訂細則，以及部分乘客在登機後，取消乘搭航班，又指單於2018年，在仁川國際機場已發生35宗與該公司有關的類似事件。為針對有關情況，公司將向所有辦理離境手續後取消其國際航班預訂的乘客，徵收每人200,000韓圜（約1,400元港幣）的額外費用。<br />\n<br />\n大韓航空批評有人「上機後退票」，令航班不必要地延誤，影響「真正的乘客」，亦不必要地浪費航空公司及機場管理局的資源，因此加強罰則。此罰則適用於從香港及菲律賓出發的航班，並待政府部門批准後即實施。<br />\n<br />\n根據韓媒報道，數名韓國人氣男團的內地及香港「粉絲」，在上周六分別購買前往韓國的頭等、商務及經濟客位機票，但他們上機與偶像見面後，在航班起飛前數分鐘，要求落機及退票。出於安全考慮，全機約360名乘客因此亦須落機重新安檢，航班終延誤約1小時。而航空公司不但要為3名「粉絲」退款，亦要就航班延誤向香港國際機場支付手續費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181218/59045008?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59045008%3F&d=jrtsyvjcMbw9rH99mlC5lMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=5901bc13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59045008%3F&h=b80d36bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181218/59045008?</a>"},{"pid":"762050a76a29437c15b1ce379b8132e2d355af49","tid":946611,"uid":40903,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒 <br />\n大家都是同鄉呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韓撚質素一單新聞睇曬"},{"pid":"b8a1872c013eb9210b9b4993f9214b2dca973500","tid":946611,"uid":134012,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"1400咁少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4687160c9e180daaeba2870b4663682bacc826","tid":946611,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁快黎料"},{"pid":"67fa2bece0530cfcbb3cbd92aad3ac424e770200","tid":946611,"uid":550,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b8a1872c013eb9210b9b4993f9214b2dca973500","tid":946611,"uid":134012,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"1400咁少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"買得頭等都唔爭在1400蚊啦泡狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fa2e59a83c71c404916d7e55293e8e77623544","tid":946611,"uid":26602,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"罰1400蚊咁少?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班fans當交稅啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf5e9ccf8635e42a32710c891f90d72a7e0c45f","tid":946611,"uid":36857,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:05:02.000Z","msg":"此罰則適用於從香港及菲律賓出發的航班，並待政府部門批准後即實施。<br />\n<br />\n香港個朵越嚟越臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝西客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4160e085ab08388fe21254e0015f5a20b66ac44d","tid":946611,"uid":41818,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3cf5e9ccf8635e42a32710c891f90d72a7e0c45f","tid":946611,"uid":36857,"like":35,"dislike"